1. *Trudi* se da završi svoj zadatak na vrijeme. (He is *trying* to finish his task on time.)
2. Ona se *trudila* da razumije sve pojmove iz knjige. (She *tried* to understand all the terms from the book.)
3. *Trudim* se da naučim nove riječi svakog dana. (I am *trying* to learn new words every day.)
4. Oni su se *trudili* da održe svoje obećanje. (They *tried* to keep their promise.)
5. *Trudiš* se previše i zato si umoran. (You are *trying* too hard and that's why you are tired.)
6. Njihova kći se *trudi* da se dokopa visokih ocjena. (Their daughter is *striving* to achieve high grades.)
7. Mi se *trudimo* da budemo što efikasniji na poslu. (We *endeavor* to be as efficient as possible at work.)
8. On *trudi* da sakrije svoju nervozu pred drugima. (He *makes an effort* to hide his nervousness from others.)